title: Soya Nutribar
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Organic, Western, Juice bar, Latin American, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Healthy food restaurant. Menu is mostly vegetarian or vegan except for a few chicken dishes. Smoothies, soymilk shakes, vegan ceviche, salad, desserts. Makes its own soymilk, coconut milk, and cashew-nut milk (this last one contains honey!). Free Wi-Fi.
streetAddress: Calle Princip, Cotiguo a Policía Turística
